	<div itemprop="text"><p>Otto, Very helpful article as always. I have a question that&#8217;s slightly off topic and am hoping someone can direct  me to a solution.</p>
<p>WP 3.1 RC1 (and prior versions) of custom taxonomies set &#8216;hierarchical&#8217; =&gt; true, won&#8217;t output a parent / child url structure. For example: if Europe is the parent and Germany the child, URLs are generated for {domain]/europe/ and [domain]/germany but not in the form [domain]/europe/germany/ </p>
