	<div itemprop="text"><p>Of course, with the necessary global $wp_query:</p>
<p><code><br />
function is_multitax() {<br />
  global $wp_query;<br />
  return count( $wp_query-&gt;tax_query-&gt;queries ) &gt; 1 );<br />
}<br />
</code></p>
</div>

