	<div itemprop="text"><p>You&#8217;re putting &#8216;posts_per_page&#8217; inside the tax_query, which makes no sense. Correct would be:</p>
<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate" title="">
$myquery['posts_per_page'] = -1;
$myquery['tax_query'] = array(
...
);
</pre>
</div>

