	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a itemprop="url" href="http://ottopress.com/2010/wordpress-3-1-advanced-taxonomy-queries/comment-page-1/#comment-9643">
		<time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2011-09-06T18:25:22+00:00">September 6, 2011 at 6:25 pm</time></a>	</div>

	<div itemprop="text"><p>You can&#8217;t do that with a native query. Taxonomy parameters affect the whole query. If you want to do it with native WP_Query objects, you&#8217;ll need to make two queries and combine the results somehow.</p>
</div>

